Title: Little River Climate Resilience
Publisher: Frost Institute for Data Science and Computing, University of Miami;https://ror.org/02dgjyy92;ROR;https://ror.org/|University of Miami Libraries, University of Miami;https://ror.org/02dgjyy92;ROR;https://ror.org/
Description: A collection of data for the study of urban climate resilience in the Little River neighborhood of Miami-Dade County. This collection serves as a set of teaching datasets for the Climate Resilience course at the Universtiy of Miami.
